name: Brookly Is Not Dead
description:
Brookly (me) was formed in 2015, and in 2018 Brookly launched the "Brookly is not dead" movement. Years later, he was attacked by the world of technology and became seriously sick.
In this art work of mine, you can see the feeling of Brookly disease, which is still called "Brookly is not dead".


I hope you like this GIF that I painted .
